summary: Jane. Female Nord. New Game Save.
descriptionHtml:
Jane, female Nord, save game. Was designed to play as my mage character. This is a clean save. No cheats or anything. It\'s saved right after the character was created at the chopping block. The uploaded picture is of her in a retextured Archmage robe.

Mods Used:

1. Detailed Faces: www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26
2. No More Blocky Faces: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
3. No Dirty Bodies - Caucasian Female: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=18
4. Amazing Smooth Females: (Smooth Females Complete \"Less smoothing then Really Smooth\" version) http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140
5. Archmage robe replaced Female Only: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=762

For the mods, I installed 1-3, then installed #4 and let it overwrite everything it asked for. You\'ll probably need to at least install #4 to get similar results.

In case anyone wants to tweak her looks at all,  I\'ve added a series of pictures during the character creation showing the bars in a separate download in a .7z file.

Installation: \\My Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves
(For Windows 7 users. Not sure where the save games go for other operating systems)

Anyways. I hope u guys like it. Enjoy.
author: McSizzle
